descriptionHtml:
Amin Taxi: It is a mobile application that provides instant or advance taxi booking service covering all governorates of Iraq and is currently available in the governorates of Baghdad, Najaf, Babylon and the Holy Karbala. Official approvals.
Amin Taxi- Smart is a smart application used by the passenger to book a taxi, which features a user-friendly interface, the application works in the city center and remote remote locations.
Taxi Amin - Where does he work? The service is currently available in Baghdad, Najaf, Babil and Karbala governorates, and we plan to expand soon.
Amin Taxi: Simple and intuitive interface
1- Download our free app
2- Open the application and log in with your name and phone number,3- Click on the “Request” option. You can move the pick-up location to the street or the place from which you want the driver to pick you up anywhere, it is easier for the driver to wait for you at the exact place
4- Choose the service: Express, Gold, State, etc...
5- Decide where you want to go. Or you can move the pin directly to the specified place or enter the exact address
6- Click to confirm the order, you will see how quickly our taxi driver will arrive. His details, photo, and vehicle details will also be displayed. You can always track your taxi driver in the app.7- Immediately after the trip, you can pay the driver in cash or through the wallet, the trip summary will be automatically sent to your email. If you have already entered it while logging in, check it out for yourself! Simply download the Taxi Amin app, sign up for free and start riding within minutes.

Amin: Where does he work? The service is currently available in Baghdad, Najaf, Babylon, and Karbala governorates, and we plan to expand soon.
Amin: Simple and intuitive interface
1- Download our free application
2- Open the application and log in with your name and phone number.
3- Click on the “Request” option. You can move the pickup location to the street or place from which you want the driver to pick you up, anywhere. It is easier for the driver to wait for you at the specified location.
4- Choose the service: Express, Savings, Gold, State, etc...
5- Select the place you want to go to. Or you can move the pin directly to the specified location or enter the exact address
6- Click to confirm the order, you will see how quickly our taxi driver will arrive. His details, photo and vehicle details will also be displayed. You can always track your taxi driver in the app.
7- Immediately after the trip, you can pay the driver in cash or through the wallet. The trip summary will be automatically sent to your email.
